name: Air Canada Embraer E-190 night takeoff from Vancouver
description:
Hey everyone, this is an onboard video of an Air Canada Embraer E-190 departing Vancouver International Airport (CYVR/YVR). I'd like to dedicate this video to SwissAirA380, who unfortunately closed his channel :( He will be missed!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
